Enum Map.Layer

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Map.Layer>
      • com.here.android.mpa.mapping.Map.Layer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Map.Layer>
    Enclosing class:
    Map
    Deprecated. 
    As of SDK 3.0. Use Map.LayerCategory instead.

    @Deprecated
public static enum Map.Layer
extends java.lang.Enum<Map.Layer>
    Definition for layers within a map. These layers can be enabled or disabled dynamically through Map.setDisplayLayers(EnumSet).

    By default, all layers are enabled.
